{"type": "article", "id": 62222, "title": "饿了么星选的春季食材动画海报不错 ，孩之宝开了家智力问答酒店 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-20T05:32:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1788, "name": "食材"}, {"id": 6547, "name": "饿了么"}, {"id": 4268, "name": "孩之宝"}, {"id": 51090, "name": "科沃斯"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190320123828fyvaDnRZeY9lgK8U.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"B5cd\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4351866907798359?\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">华为新机型 P30 拍了 3 支广告片宣传摄影功能。</a>片中找来拍摄对象来展示感光能力、长焦和双景录像这些卖点，</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y0851upwnbp\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b0851eke0yn\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j0851ffb2f0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"B5cd\"><b><a href=\"http:// https://www.designboom.com/art/tom-sachs-mcdonalds-graphic-standards-03-19-2019/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">现代艺术家 Tom Sachs 创作了“麦当劳员工手册”。</a></b>它是 2018 年 <em>McDonald’s Graphic Standards</em> 的特别版。手册中绘制了汉堡的构成和制作方法、厨师服装、菜单、必备工具甚至是卫生间的卷纸。不过最吸睛的饰有 Logo 的白手套和木箱包装盒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320123932LNWBug0li1d4nGIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320123932t0iaDjLQVZCIU6Ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903201239322T9zvbSYAwQWyK8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320123932AL0UI9wypef2rGsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320123932gyskhWf10L6jzJ5M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320123932bGI8Ft7mc31zV4iP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"aDK9\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=isbQsEfSeJc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>孩之宝将要在俄罗斯莫斯科开了一家 Trivial Pursuit 酒店。</b></a>它把棋盘游戏搬到了现实生活中，酒店从预订到具体住宿房型，全都取决于回答问题的质量。例如预定时会问参与者拿破仑的身高和以“莫斯科”命名的河流。酒店将于今年 5 月 20 日-- 6 月 14 日开放，创意代理商是 Leo Burnet/Moscow。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0851128npq\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Cuu7\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ouyv2mWQCro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>梅奥诊所在广告中展示了患者的就医前心情。</b></a>片中捕捉了他们面对或严重或复杂诊断的未知感，而梅奥诊所是他们旅程中“确定”的地方，既是目的地更能获得诊断答案。创意代理商是TBWA /Chiat/Day New York。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0851qudnex\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p0851l6rjul\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=m0851zzwosg\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Up8M\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzY3ODY2Mw==&amp;mid=2247494166&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3ad815c02654e289fa83d028470cf06e&amp;chksm=fbed883ecc9a0128123ecdf91048626691b6dcf9ce36a4f0bebd1456dee77a1a8a36ca896fe7&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0320rahpGqbQZnU72WsHkV9w&amp;key=d2e42a84cf84ae840f5717f3d37e746d07dda4413629a87a6fb690ac91371b71020d02d8421cd8f80b49424f524743755572da7783dc3093899cb83e36936a9cac714259bd0bc6e1fa7a129808e1b93d&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=e98ztnBHz0H5d1c3hg3JZ%2FBKfCww3l0D%2B5syG3p%2BJ0Afbdf4%2F2W0PEPmXc1ja47Z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">饿了么星选以春季食材为主题制作了一系列动画广告。</a></b>海报上把饿了么星选上的食材和生长环境融合在了一起，来突出新鲜的特点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124152RkEI39uOfJQdB6PV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124153HTDU7aRrLVIWGqvk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563596\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124317hCTAiYKytjoEfzLJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124153qwTv24HfPWjQY65M.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124152BbVJG1h6cyCLKlm8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h0851mzhkho\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"428Z\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA4MTE2MA==&amp;mid=2650278555&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=22a29d6a9bdfcb5a4a755097c86535d2&amp;chksm=beb65d3c89c1d42abbd8c73a2aef393e1fece2e5fd243309bbf35bd96dcbbf043cf6c2919616&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0320lJ0d8MaYCbUyuzMhJBJq&amp;key=e26fe09897582c5852cc6184880fc7dd648461c16917f4aa0ec86f71f596eea5d6757af56f705c3157cf8601a8f36868f180f2fb8bcbdad2ec5b0a84dd0fd00716e5dcc71b51582d5ded289c2d8f99ca&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=e98ztnBHz0H5d1c3hg3JZ%2FBKfCww3l0D%2B5syG3p%2BJ0Afbdf4%2F2W0PEPmXc1ja47Z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">网易 LOFTER 制作了支“有点才华公司” H5。</a></b>这家公司设有表面财富自由部、柠檬制造工厂等，参与者完成“笔试”回答相应部门的问题，然后生成公司门牌。每个部门都和 LOFTER 上的兴趣领域有关。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124221nb8seQW7apcf34kS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124645ajTuPhBNXDyE9VfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190320124221ZcfPRnHTxtDkjIug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.710667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"uiTF\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTQwODE2NA==&amp;mid=2649694366&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b57259c9154104da94cbcf75b443f6b7&amp;chksm=bf2067d58857eec30953666723a60c4184685358549cad162f224cac5b33af2554e16d2a3f07&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0320gVzwBsIM2nEhimu9xnha&amp;key=e26fe09897582c587074c2a4ca0e9f66dc61447e9ccadc6aeb2b5b1213e426323c6b0650fdd2fb740ae0876627bbbc27aa2824e1209a297918dcf23d3d59fbe548907fcde40961f0878d60124a0ad245&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=e98ztnBHz0H5d1c3hg3JZ%2FBKfCww3l0D%2B5syG3p%2BJ0Afbdf4%2F2W0PEPmXc1ja47Z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>科沃斯找来彭昱畅演绎不同人群的洁癖特点。</b></a>他在片中一人分饰四角，普通居家男孩、教父、侦探和卓别林，他们都是如何把职业特点发挥在洁癖上的。结尾引出智能扫地机器人的优势。同时，科沃斯和 GQ 实验室合作发布了漫画展现生活中的“精神洁癖”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0851ukqxxi\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"OWiw\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MjAxNDM4MA==&amp;mid=2666244352&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=41f85ce781a4d85a892caa3328efaca5&amp;chksm=bdb3c0438ac44955a15564bf6e4bb2489b7ed6f3f004fda93b2ae16db3595589e8836fd9bb60&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=&amp;key=579ba6bfe709a41a592a597ce69ccc52312443cf5f025a1defff04730378608276cff3ddf1dd73eac2079638f801d49495ca0087fa77fb58a142e91f76a7d1ed0fac5dfddfc8bc502d8319256ac67199&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=e98ztnBHz0H5d1c3hg3JZ%2FBKfCww3l0D%2B5syG3p%2BJ0Afbdf4%2F2W0PEPmXc1ja47Z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>国家广播电视总局 3 月 18 日要求停止播放部分广告。</b></a>涉及到“椰树牌椰汁”，“力补金秋胶囊”和“强身牌四子填精胶囊”的部分版本。它认为椰树牌椰汁的广告在价值观导向上存在偏差，尤其是会对未成年人产生误导，</p><p line=\"2r6I\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2019/03/20/bcw-wins-pr-business-of-lenovo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>博雅公关获得联想中国的公关代理业务。</b></a>联想一直是和蓝色光标合作，去年 7 月，联想召集多家公关代理公司比稿。博雅会负责企业形象公关，还包括一些产品公关项目、思想领导力和企业危机管理。与此同时，蓝色光标依然在联想的公关服务商之中。</p><p line=\"2r6I\" class=\"\"><br></p><p line=\"2r6I\" class=\"\">题图来自：<a spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1-6WaSYKHEnviOwd4DEn3A\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Trivial Pursuit Hotel</a></p><p><br></p>"}